  "short_description": "DEPO is a first person 3D platformer where you control a rebel pixel inside a computer with an evil Operating System governing everything. You'll find final bosses, cinematic scenes, arcade mini-games, 70 huge levels full of surprises, ¡and big stories to discover!",
