  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/4362765f563e8e2517bec65afd17841d.avif?t=1768253690\" width=618 height=82 /></span><br>Step into the shoes of a pixel inside a computer system on the brink of collapse. Explore dozens of colorful worlds and crazy files to uncover and thwart the evil plan of EYE.CO. Discover the lives and secrets of other pixels—everyone's hiding something... <strong>Can you save the System?</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/11c4de2794fbead16fe3afad7f092385.avif?t=1768253690\" width=618 height=82 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🧭 EXPLORATION GALORE!</strong></h2>DEPO is packed with details and rewards for the most adventurous explorers. A wide variety of unique worlds and files await you, each one completely distinct.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>💬 A STORY FULL OF SECRETS!</strong></h2>Every pixel in the System hides mysterious secrets, and getting to know them is key to understanding the world of DEPO. They will all change throughout your journey, revealing new information. Unraveling these mysteries won't be easy...<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/87e345384a55dcb7803742c747de1868.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/87e345384a55dcb7803742c747de1868.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/87e345384a55dcb7803742c747de1868.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>👑 DRESS TO IMPRESS</strong></h2>Customize your pixel's appearance with dozens of outfits and personalize your own guided missile.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🌐 PLAY WITH FRIENDS AND OTHER PLAYERS ONLINE</strong></h2>Complete the story mode with other players, chat with them, and trade items.<br><strong>It's even more fun with friends!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3eae026fc97e55ee8cfe502ac013d677.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=148 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3eae026fc97e55ee8cfe502ac013d677.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3eae026fc97e55ee8cfe502ac013d677.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🎮 REPLAYABILITY!</strong></h2>DEPO's postgame content is extensive and packed with new adventures, offering hours and hours of entertainment even after you complete the main story! It's almost like getting a new game!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⏱️ TIME TRIAL MODE</strong></h2>Each file in DEPO has a time trial mode where you can race against Bill, the fastest pixel in the System. Train and find hundreds of shortcuts to achieve incredible speeds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/8b2908a6741c752ff9190ad4f346728e.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/8b2908a6741c752ff9190ad4f346728e.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/8b2908a6741c752ff9190ad4f346728e.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>⚽ MULTIPLAYER MINIGAMES</strong></h2>As if the story mode wasn't enough, you'll also find 5 frantic multiplayer minigames where your friendships will be put to the test...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🛠️ LEVEL EDITOR</strong></h2>You can also create your own levels and share them with the community. Let your creativity run wild.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3bb0c9b35abc343bcfa9a62e88682e1d.poster.avif?t=1768253690\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3bb0c9b35abc343bcfa9a62e88682e1d.webm?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/3bb0c9b35abc343bcfa9a62e88682e1d.mp4?t=1768253690\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Join the DEPO community on Discord by clicking in the social networks on the right 👉🏼👉🏼</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1091320/extras/298b85644618eea74770be2b539fb9a2.avif?t=1768253690\" width=569 height=82 /></span>",
